    • download

      public void download(jakarta.xml.soap.SOAPConnection conn) throws jakarta.xml.soap.SOAPException
      Depending of the state of this Solicitude this method will call the request download service; then the verify request service; and all the download package requests needed in order to do the downloads of this Solicitude.

      Since a Solicitude has a state and updates it as it performs service requests, this method can use that state to continue the download process were it left.

      Note: If this Solicitude is paused, this method unpauses it.

      Parameters:
      conn - the connection to use
      Throws:
      jakarta.xml.soap.SOAPException - if there were SOAP related problems
      IllegalArgumentException - if conn is null
      jakarta.xml.ws.WebServiceException - if there were other service related problems
